posting_body: ['The perfect combination of privacy, luxury and maintenance free living to satisfy your lifestyle!', 'Find quintessential homes with our well-thought-out collection of floor plans, suitable for a simple and minimalistic lifestyle.', 'Our spacious detached homes include private backyards and resort-style amenities in a serene suburban community.', 'Bring along your furry friends we are a pet-friendly community with no breed restrictions!', 'Amenties:', 'Private Backyard', 'Front Porch/Private Entrance', 'Open Floor Plans', 'High Ceilings', 'Wood Plank Style Flooring Throughout', 'Granite Countertops', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Ceiling Fans', 'Walk-In Closets', 'Fireplace In Select Homes', 'Full Size Washer/Dryer', 'Call or Text Tyler to set up your for Fast Personal Showings or Virtual Showings!', '*Restrictions Apply.', 'Pricing, availability and lease terms subject to change anytime!']
